<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Invitation - {{orderTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            margin: -30px -30px 20px -30px;
        }
        .order-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }
        .business-info {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6c3;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .info-item {
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background-color: #ffeaa7;
            color: #d63031;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ü§ù Order Invitation</h1>
            <p>You've been invited to collaborate on a new order</p>
        </div>

        <h2> Hello üëã ,  </h2>
        
        <p>You have been invited to participate in a new order created by <strong>{{businessName}}</strong>. Here are the details:</p>

        <div class="order-details">
            <h3>üìã Order Information</h3>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Order Title</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{orderTitle}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Order ID</div>
                    <div class="info-value">#{{orderNumber}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if orderDescription}}
            <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <div class="info-label">Description</div>
                <div class="info-value">{{orderDescription}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if startDate}}
            <div class="info-grid" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Start Date</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{startDate}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if endDate}}
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">End Date</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{endDate}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="business-info">
            <h3>üè¢ Business Information</h3>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Business Name</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{businessName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Contact Person</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{vendorName}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if businessEmail}}
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Email</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{businessEmail}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if businessPhone}}
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Phone</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{businessPhone}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <h3>Ready to get started?</h3>
            <p>Click the button below to view the order details and decide whether to accept or decline this invitation (You might
                have to sign up to view this order):</p>
            
            <a style="cursor: pointer;" href="{{invitationLink}}" class="cta-button">View Order Details</a>
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
            <strong>üîí Security Notice:</strong> This invitation is valid for <strong>7 days</strong> from the date it was sent. After this period, you'll need to request a new invitation from the vendor.
        </div>

        <h3>What happens next?</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Review the order:</strong> Click the link above to see full order details</li>
            <li><strong>Accept or decline:</strong> Let {{businessName}} know your decision</li>
            <li><strong>Start collaborating:</strong> If accepted, you can begin working on the order</li>
            <li><strong>Secure payment:</strong> All payments are processed securely through PayBud</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Need Help?</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions about this order or need assistance:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>üìß Contact the vendor directly: {{#if businessEmail}}{{businessEmail}}{{else}}Available in order details{{/if}}</li>
            <li>üí¨ PayBud Support: support@paybud.com</li>
            {{!-- <li>üìö Help Center: <a href="{{helpCenterUrl}}">paybud.com/help</a></li> --}}
        </ul>

        <p>We're here to ensure a smooth and secure collaboration experience!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The PayBud Team</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                This invitation was sent to {{clientEmail}} by {{businessName}}<br>
                If you believe this was sent in error, please contact our support team.
            </p>
            
            <p>¬© 2024 PayBud. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
